FT  21 JUL 93 / Parliament and Politics: Dublin angered by Tebbit remarks
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE Irish government is to raise with Britain remarks made by Lord Tebbit
about bomb attacks on Dublin.
During a Sky TV programme on Monday night on Ireland's controversial
constitutional territorial claim on Ulster, the former Conservative party
chairman declared: 'I suspect that the only thing that will take that out of
