FT  21 JUL 93 / Call over Scottish coal industry
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A GROUP of former coal managers, industrialists and union leaders have set
up a company to try to buy the Scottish coal industry.
Mining Scotland is pressing the government to separate British Coal's
Scottish assets from the rest.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
</XX>
<CO>Mining Scotland.
    British Coal Corp.
